spec_data.Name: python2-repoze-sphinx-autointerface
spec_data.Description:
This package defines an extension for the Sphinx documentation system.
The extension allows generation of API documentation by introspection of
zope.interface instances in code.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 03:30:45 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Auto-generate Sphinx API docs from Zope interfaces
